column2: "Ah, you're back. I've had a chance to look at your report. You did well, hm?"
"If you can keep on using Twin Daggers like that, you won't have anything to worry about."
"You may keep those Twin Daggers. Consider them a farewell gift."
"That's all I can teach you. Keep on practicing with those Twin Daggers."

"New Client Orders are available for Barbara.

Barbara can be found in the Gate Area, second floor."
